    <item>
      <title>英国央行以 5:4 投票决定降息，但未透露下一步行动时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/boe-cuts-rates-in-5-4-vote-and-offers-no-timing-on-next-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行自 2020 年初以来首次降息，并暗示未来将进一步谨慎降息，在英国经历了一代人以来最高的借贷成本之后，这一举措为家庭带来了一些缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/boe-cuts-rates-in-5-4-vote-and-offers-no-timing-on-next-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗保险部门利润下降，业绩不及预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/apollo-misses-estimates-as-profit-drops-at-athene-insurance-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 公布的第二季度业绩不及华尔街预期，因为更高的费用未能抵消其 Athene 年金业务利润的下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/apollo-misses-estimates-as-profit-drops-at-athene-insurance-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:32:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟和乌克兰驳斥匈牙利石油恐慌，称过境运输正常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/eu-rebuffs-hungary-s-request-for-meeting-on-lukoil-transit-ban</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟拒绝了匈牙利和斯洛伐克对乌克兰制裁俄罗斯一家大型石油公司的担忧，并暂时拒绝了他们就原油供应安全进行紧急磋商的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/eu-rebuffs-hungary-s-request-for-meeting-on-lukoil-transit-ban</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 10:24:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼旗舰业务利润因机场和采矿业务增长 115%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/adani-flagship-s-profit-surges-115-on-airports-mining-revenue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆·阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 的旗舰企业阿达尼企业 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 公布季度利润增长 115%，得益于其机场和采矿业务的稳健收入，该企业在去年遭受了严厉的卖空者攻击后有所反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/adani-flagship-s-profit-surges-115-on-airports-mining-revenue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 09:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 坚持减产计划 中东紧张局势导致油价继续上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，伊朗已下令对以色列实施报复性打击，以报复在其领土上杀害一名哈马斯领导人，而 OPEC+ 暗示不会改变其下个季度恢复暂停生产的计划，油价因此进一步上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 23:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
